---
import Features3 from '~/components/widgets/Features3.astro';
import Hero from '~/components/widgets/Hero.astro';
import PricingSection from '~/components/widgets/PricingSection.astro';
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import LetsStart from '~/components/widgets/LetsStart.astro';
import PaymentWidget from '~/components/widgets/PaymentWidget.astro';
import BlogLatestPosts from '~/components/widgets/BlogLatestPosts.astro';
import Image from '~/components/common/Image.astro';
import techWeLove from '~/assets/images/tech-we-love.png';

const metadata = {
  title: 'Services',
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <!-- Hero Widget ******************* -->

  <Hero
    tagline="Transforming Your Business Online"
    image={{
      src: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1559136555-9303baea8ebd',
      alt: 'Business Transformation Image',
    }}
  >
    <Fragment slot="title">
      Bring your <span class="text-accent dark:text-white highlight">business idea</span> to life,<br />
      launch it in just <span class="text-accent dark:text-white highlight">90 days</span>
    </Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="subtitle">
      Explore our packages or hire us for ongoing development to bring your project to fruition.
    </Fragment>
  </Hero>

  <!-- MVP Development ******************* -->
  <section id="mvp-development">
    <PricingSection
      id="MVP"
      title="Code & Mentoring - MVP in 90 Days"
      subtitle="Transform your idea into a successful product with our comprehensive MVP development program. Our team will guide you through every step, from initial concept to post-launch optimization."
      url="/start"
    >
      <table class="w-full">
        <tr class="h-8 text-xl">
          <td colspan="2"><strong>Package Price</strong></td>
          <td><strong>$45.0K</strong></td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mt-4">
        Our MVP program is structured over 12 weeks to ensure comprehensive development and successful launch. Here’s a
        breakdown of the program:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-lg text-gray-700 mt-4">
        <li>
          <strong>Week 1:</strong> Clarifying Vision - Define the project goals, target audience, and key features.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Week 2-3:</strong> Design, UX, and Prototyping - Create initial wireframes and prototypes to visualize
          the product.
        </li>
        <li><strong>Week 3-9:</strong> Development - Begin coding and building the core features of the MVP.</li>
        <li>
          <strong>Week 9-10:</strong> Testing - Conduct thorough testing to identify and fix bugs and ensure functionality.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Week 11:</strong> Pre-Launch - Prepare for launch, including final adjustments and marketing strategies.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Week 12:</strong> Launch and Post-Launch Support - Launch the MVP and provide ongoing support and optimization.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mt-4">
        <strong>Client:</strong> "<i
          >What truly set this team apart was their incredible communication and collaborative approach. They didn't
          just develop our MVP; they worked alongside us, transforming our concept with incredible insight and
          responsiveness. In just 90 days, they turned our startup vision into a pretty awesome app.</i
        >" - Radhika Sharma, CEO, InnovateNow
      </p>
    </PricingSection>
  </section>

  <!-- Development Packages ******************* -->
  <section id="development-packages">
    <PaymentWidget
      title="Comprehensive Development Services"
      description="Our full-service agency offers design, UX, development, marketing, SEO, and more. Ideal for ongoing projects and continuous development. Feed the backlog and watch your project progress."
      items={[
        {
          name: 'Essential Care (S)',
          description:
            'Reliable ongoing support for maintenance, updates, and small-scale tasks. Ideal for keeping your project running smoothly and updated with the latest needs. Examples include fixing bugs, updating content, implementing minor feature enhancements, and ensuring compatibility with new technologies.',
          url: '/start',
          payment: '$995 per week',
        },
        {
          name: 'Pair Dev (M)',
          description:
            'A focused two-person team for MVP creation and small-scale projects, delivering design and development expertise in a compact, agile package. Examples of tasks include developing core features, implementing user authentication, integrating third-party APIs, creating responsive UI components, conducting code reviews, and optimizing performance.',
          url: '/start',
          payment: '$2450 per week',
        },
        {
          name: 'Core Build Team (L)',
          description:
            'A dedicated team of developers and strategists collaborating to deliver high-quality, scalable solutions for medium to large projects. Perfect for startups and businesses ready to scale. Our team handles comprehensive documentation, creates robust design systems, and posts regular updates to keep you informed. We also provide weekly video summaries of features delivered to ensure transparency and alignment with your goals.',
          url: '/start',
          payment: '$4000 per week',
        },
        {
          name: 'Full-Scale Execution (XL)',
          description:
            'Comprehensive full-time team engagement for complex, high-stakes projects requiring end-to-end development, robust testing, and ongoing refinement. This package includes everything mentioned above but with a more intense focus from a full team dedicated to your project, ensuring maximum efficiency and quality.',
          url: '/start',
          payment: '$8000 per week',
        },
        {
          name: 'Marketing Automation & Content',
          description:
            'Full LinkedIn, Instagram, and Facebook automation setup and support, including content creation for these platforms. We also handle the setup of funnels and landing pages, as well as email sequences to ensure a seamless marketing strategy. This comprehensive package is designed to maximize your online presence and engagement.',
          url: '/start',
          payment: '$1500(M) / $2500(L) per month',
        },
      ]}
    >
      />
    </PaymentWidget>

    <!-- General Terms and Conditions ******************* -->
    <Features3
      id="terms"
      title="General Terms and Conditions"
      subtitle="Experience the Benefits of Our Plans"
      columns={2}
      items={[
        {
          title: 'Transparent Pricing',
          description:
            'We charge in advance for each 2-week sprint. The price is fixed and will not change during the project. Payments are required ahead of each sprint.',
          icon: 'tabler:premium-rights',
        },
        {
          title: 'Flexible Scheduling',
          description:
            'We schedule sprints based on your readiness to receive work. If you need to pause or delay funding, we will resume when slots are available.',
          icon: 'tabler:calendar-month',
        },
        {
          title: 'Structured Process',
          description:
            'Each sprint begins with a planning session (IPM) and concludes with a brief retrospective and a demo of the completed work.',
          icon: 'tabler:refresh',
        },
        {
          title: 'Continuous Feedback',
          description:
            'We value your feedback on partial work or features during the sprint. Timely feedback helps us adjust and align the work with your needs.',
          icon: 'tabler:rotate',
        },
      ]}
      classes={{ container: 'max-w-5xl' }}
    />

    <PricingSection id="AI" title="AI Training for Techies" url="/start">
      <Fragment slot="explain">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
          We are excited to offer a new training program designed to help organizations apply AI in development. This
          structured and clear approach will guide you through the process of integrating AI into your projects.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
          The training spans 3 weeks, with 3-4 workshops per week. You will learn how to apply AI in your projects and
          lead AI initiatives. The curriculum covers developing requirements, creating prototypes, producing design
          systems, structuring applications, writing code and tests, creating database models, and planning
          deployments—all with the help of AI.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
          This program is ideal for lead developers, product owners, and other senior roles within your organization.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mt-4">
          <strong>Testimonial:</strong> "The AI training program was a game-changer for our team. We walked away with two
          critical skills that have transformed our workflow: AI-powered code generation, which cuts our development time
          by 30%, and intelligent debugging tools that help us catch and resolve issues much faster. It wasn't just training—it
          was a practical roadmap for integrating AI into our development process. We learned a lot while enjoying every
          moment." - Michael Harris, Product Owner at Stealth Startup
        </p>
      </Fragment>
    </PricingSection>

    <!-- Technical Coaching ******************* -->
