          </p>

          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
            If you’re feeling stuck or overwhelmed, these sessions will provide the clarity and support needed to move
            forward with confidence. As an action coach, I focus on overcoming roadblocks, simplifying complex
            processes, and driving results. Together, we’ll ensure you have more time, reduced stress, and increased
